00:18:42.860 --> 00:18:43.620
Zhou Xiao.

00:18:44.460 --> 00:18:45.860
This is Zhao Fanzhou's mom calling you.

00:18:46.060 --> 00:18:46.900
Do you still remember me?

00:18:47.380 --> 00:18:48.140
Of course I do.

00:18:48.420 --> 00:18:50.340
How have your body recovered recently?

00:18:51.460 --> 00:18:52.380
It has almost fully recovered.

00:18:52.380 --> 00:18:53.660
I have been discharged from the hospital.

00:18:53.940 --> 00:18:55.300
Then I have been busy tidying up our house.

00:18:55.380 --> 00:18:57.300
Thus, I didn't call you till now.

00:18:58.820 --> 00:18:59.940
Am I disturbing you?

00:19:00.140 --> 00:19:00.940
No, you are not.

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:03.020
I am supposed to pay you a visit.

00:19:03.340 --> 00:19:04.620
Then why haven't you come?

00:19:04.900 --> 00:19:05.420
Huh?

00:19:07.500 --> 00:19:08.100
Zhou Xiao,

00:19:09.100 --> 00:19:09.980
I know

00:19:10.220 --> 00:19:11.700
what happened between you and Fanzhou.

00:19:12.460 --> 00:19:14.340
But I really like you.

00:19:14.940 --> 00:19:16.260
I regard you as a friend.

00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:19.020
Could our relation remain unchanged

00:19:19.380 --> 00:19:21.060
despite such a happening?

00:19:23.340 --> 00:19:24.180
Yes.

00:19:26.340 --> 00:19:27.220
That's great!

00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:28.740
It happens to be the weekend.

00:19:28.860 --> 00:19:30.100
I have made the soup.

00:19:30.420 --> 00:19:31.700
Come and have lunch with me.

00:19:31.700 --> 00:19:33.100
I will send you the address
of our home, all right?

00:19:33.780 --> 00:19:34.940
But I...

00:19:35.180 --> 00:19:36.220
Well,

00:19:36.820 --> 00:19:37.940
don't worry.

00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:39.380
Just the two of us.

00:19:42.740 --> 00:19:44.340
OK. I got it, Mrs. Zhao.

00:20:09.460 --> 00:20:10.380
Hello, Mrs. Zhao!

00:20:10.660 --> 00:20:11.420
Glad to see you, Zhou Xiao.

00:20:12.460 --> 00:20:13.340
Come on in!

00:20:19.140 --> 00:20:21.220
Three, four.

00:20:22.620 --> 00:20:23.940
You are good at this.

00:20:25.020 --> 00:20:25.580
Mrs. Zhao.

00:20:25.620 --> 00:20:26.020
Yes?

00:20:26.220 --> 00:20:27.220
When shall we have the meal?

00:20:27.740 --> 00:20:29.220
No need to rush.
Help me clear the game first.

00:20:32.580 --> 00:20:34.220
But the food has been served.

00:20:34.260 --> 00:20:35.220
It will get cold if not eaten.

00:20:35.660 --> 00:20:36.660
Let me finish this game.

00:20:37.020 --> 00:20:37.460
OK.

00:20:40.700 --> 00:20:41.260
Someone is arriving.

00:20:41.580 --> 00:20:42.980
Huh? Who is it?

00:20:46.140 --> 00:20:48.060
I will go check who is coming.

00:20:48.100 --> 00:20:48.580
OK.

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:55.140
Mom, I am back.

00:20:56.340 --> 00:20:56.980
Fanzhou,

00:20:57.340 --> 00:20:59.100
