00:20:59.140 --> 00:20:59.860
You asked me...

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:03.060
Why didn't you call me before coming back?

00:21:03.060 --> 00:21:05.580
I have invited Zhou Xiao over
to have a meal today.

00:21:12.740 --> 00:21:13.300
Zhou Xiao,

00:21:14.420 --> 00:21:15.260
I am sorry!

00:21:15.260 --> 00:21:17.100
I really didn't know he would come back.

00:21:17.540 --> 00:21:19.740
If you feel embarrassed,

00:21:20.020 --> 00:21:20.900
I will ask him to leave.

00:21:21.180 --> 00:21:21.860
Go! Go! Go!

00:21:22.500 --> 00:21:23.180
Leave here.

00:21:23.180 --> 00:21:24.100
It's all right, Mrs. Zhao.

00:21:27.620 --> 00:21:28.180
Really?

00:21:29.100 --> 00:21:29.620
Yes.

00:21:29.660 --> 00:21:30.220
It doesn't matter.

00:21:31.300 --> 00:21:32.660
Then we can have the meal together.

00:21:34.220 --> 00:21:34.500
Come on!

00:21:35.500 --> 00:21:36.540
Come on! Let's eat together.

00:21:36.540 --> 00:21:37.260
Sit here.

00:21:37.940 --> 00:21:38.380
Come on.

00:21:38.380 --> 00:21:38.980
Here.

00:21:42.260 --> 00:21:42.860
Fanzhou.

00:21:42.940 --> 00:21:43.460
Take a seat.

00:21:43.580 --> 00:21:44.020
Hmm.

00:21:44.300 --> 00:21:45.180
Come on. Sit here.

00:21:48.740 --> 00:21:49.780
I am back.

00:21:52.740 --> 00:21:53.380
Dad.

00:21:54.180 --> 00:21:54.740
Oh!

00:21:55.700 --> 00:21:56.980
You are all here.

00:21:58.020 --> 00:21:59.900
Why do you

00:21:59.900 --> 00:22:00.620
come back so unexpectedly?

00:22:01.740 --> 00:22:03.460
Our company gave us some mooncakes
for the Mid-Autumn Festival.

00:22:03.500 --> 00:22:04.300
So I brought them home.

00:22:05.140 --> 00:22:05.740
Hello, Mr. Zhao!

00:22:06.860 --> 00:22:08.260
She is Zhou Xiao. You have met her before.

00:22:08.420 --> 00:22:08.980
Yes, I know her.

00:22:09.300 --> 00:22:10.380
It has been a long time
since we met last time.

00:22:13.380 --> 00:22:13.900
Fanzhou,

00:22:14.740 --> 00:22:16.380
why is your face so red?

00:22:17.340 --> 00:22:18.140
Aah!

00:22:18.900 --> 00:22:20.820
Fanzhou is in front of the girl he loves.

00:22:20.820 --> 00:22:21.820
Surely, he blushes.

00:22:22.460 --> 00:22:23.860
Why can't you see?

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:24.340
Well,

00:22:24.700 --> 00:22:26.180
he never blushes.

00:22:26.180 --> 00:22:27.380
He is like me in this aspect.

00:22:28.380 --> 00:22:29.420
Could it be possible that you've got a fever?

00:22:31.020 --> 00:22:31.940
It really feels hot.

00:22:31.940 --> 00:22:33.580
Touch it. Come over. Come over.

00:22:38.420 --> 00:22:39.420
When I called you,

00:22:39.420 --> 00:22:40.580
you told me you were fine, right?

00:22:41.140 --> 00:22:42.260
How come you have got injured?

00:22:42.380 --> 00:22:43.500
Moreover, your wound is inflamed.

00:22:43.980 --> 00:22:45.380
What happened on earth?

00:22:46.620 --> 00:22:47.340
It's nothing.

00:22:47.780 --> 00:22:49.300
Something fell down suddenly

00:22:49.300 --> 00:22:50.060
and I was hit out of carelessness.

00:22:50.860 --> 00:22:52.620
Why didn't you dodge?

00:23:01.580 --> 00:23:03.300
You two are hiding something from me, right?

00:23:04.660 --> 00:23:05.260
Zhou Xiao,

00:23:05.460 --> 00:23:06.180
tell me what it is.

00:23:06.540 --> 00:23:07.100
Don't mind him.

00:23:09.740 --> 00:23:10.420
Mrs. Zhao,

00:23:11.220 --> 00:23:12.100
he

00:23:12.860 --> 00:23:13.780
saved someone.

00:23:15.660 --> 00:23:17.300
It is a good deed to save others.

00:23:17.300 --> 00:23:18.900
Why were you hesitating to tell it?

00:23:19.580 --> 00:23:20.580
He has been like this since childhood.

00:23:20.700 --> 00:23:22.260
Whenever he did a good deed,
he didn't tell others.

00:23:23.260 --> 00:23:24.060
Tell me.

00:23:24.220 --> 00:23:25.260
Whom has he saved?

00:23:26.460 --> 00:23:26.940
Mrs. Zhao.

00:23:29.940 --> 00:23:30.500
It was me.

00:23:33.380 --> 00:23:34.060
You?

00:23:36.100 --> 00:23:37.420
He saved me.

00:23:42.660 --> 00:23:43.260
Zhou Xiao.

00:23:45.660 --> 00:23:47.100
In my son's mind,

00:23:47.860 --> 00:23:49.100
you're more important than himself.

00:23:55.220 --> 00:23:57.580
Mrs. Zhao, I'd better leave now for today.

00:23:57.620 --> 00:23:58.740
I will come to visit you some other day.

00:23:58.980 --> 00:23:59.620
Why should you?

00:24:00.380 --> 00:24:00.860
Then I will see you off.

00:24:00.860 --> 00:24:01.660
Stay a little longer.

00:24:02.580 --> 00:24:02.900
Zhou Xiao.

00:24:02.900 --> 00:24:03.660
I found it. I found it.

00:24:03.820 --> 00:24:04.580
I found it.

00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:05.660
Here is the anti-inflammatory drug.

00:24:14.020 --> 00:24:14.820
It is expired.

00:24:15.700 --> 00:24:16.420
Is it?

00:24:17.820 --> 00:24:18.500
Is it expired?

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:19.780
Well, I didn't...

00:24:21.860 --> 00:24:23.100
It is expired.

00:24:23.700 --> 00:24:24.060
Oh.

00:24:24.660 --> 00:24:25.940
I didn't see clearly.

00:24:26.620 --> 00:24:27.700
What should we do?

00:24:27.860 --> 00:24:29.180
Go buy some new drug.

00:24:29.540 --> 00:24:30.100
Let's go.

00:24:30.260 --> 00:24:30.900
Well, Mrs. Zhao,

00:24:31.020 --> 00:24:32.100
how about I go to buy the drug?

00:24:34.060 --> 00:24:36.100
You must drive a car
even if going to the nearest drugstore.

00:24:36.580 --> 00:24:37.460
We'd better go buy the drug.

00:24:38.740 --> 00:24:39.260
Right. Exactly.

00:24:39.860 --> 00:24:41.500
Help me take care of Fanzhou.

00:24:41.660 --> 00:24:42.780
Don't let him fall in a faint.

00:24:42.820 --> 00:24:43.300
All right?

00:24:46.700 --> 00:24:47.860
Then we are leaving.

00:24:47.860 --> 00:24:48.300
Let's go.

00:24:55.420 --> 00:24:56.020
Oops!

00:24:57.700 --> 00:24:58.540
I feel very dizzy.

00:24:59.980 --> 00:25:01.100
Take a seat.

00:25:01.500 --> 00:25:01.980
Hmm.

00:25:12.780 --> 00:25:17.180
(Lock Status)

00:25:17.220 --> 00:25:17.940
What are you doing?

00:25:18.540 --> 00:25:19.900
I locked the door from outside.

00:25:20.100 --> 00:25:21.140
Thus, they won't be able to get out.

00:25:27.860 --> 00:25:28.660
Are you all right?

00:25:30.940 --> 00:25:32.420
I am fine, but feel a bit dizzy.

00:25:35.780 --> 00:25:37.100
Do you want to drink some water?

00:25:37.140 --> 00:25:37.660
I will fetch some water for you.

00:25:38.340 --> 00:25:38.820
OK.

00:25:51.820 --> 00:25:52.460
Mengjun,

00:25:52.780 --> 00:25:53.660
today

00:25:53.740 --> 00:25:55.020
you have put on an excellent performance.

00:25:55.740 --> 00:25:56.180
Good!

00:25:57.820 --> 00:25:59.620
I have figured out what to say

00:25:59.620 --> 00:26:00.740
to make them get back together.

00:26:01.140 --> 00:26:02.940
I didn't expect you came uninvited.

00:26:03.100 --> 00:26:04.180
I have to improvise in my action.

00:26:07.020 --> 00:26:07.660
Zhao Jian,

00:26:08.580 --> 00:26:09.860
when you are free,

00:26:10.500 --> 00:26:12.060
I hope you can prepare the divorce agreement.

00:26:14.060 --> 00:26:14.580
Mengjun...

00:26:14.980 --> 00:26:15.660
Well,

00:26:17.140 --> 00:26:19.820
we have been torturing each other
for so long.

00:26:20.860 --> 00:26:21.860
I have made up my mind.

00:26:23.460 --> 00:26:24.380
Mengjun, listen to me.

00:26:24.380 --> 00:26:24.820
Enough.

00:26:26.740 --> 00:26:27.460
Stop talking.

00:27:10.300 --> 00:27:11.980
Anyway, Mrs. Zhao won't pick up the phone,

00:27:13.060 --> 00:27:14.060
and you are running a fever.

00:27:14.060 --> 00:27:15.300
I'd better go buy the drug for you.

00:27:16.140 --> 00:27:16.740
I will go with you.

00:27:17.660 --> 00:27:18.780
You are running a fever. You don't need to.

00:27:19.060 --> 00:27:19.580
Then I will escort you out.

00:27:25.860 --> 00:27:27.620
Wait a sec.
I will finish putting on my shoes soon.

00:27:28.140 --> 00:27:29.820
I've said that you need not follow me.

00:27:31.420 --> 00:27:32.140
Wait for me for a moment.

00:27:35.300 --> 00:27:36.060
Zhao Fanzhou,

00:27:37.460 --> 00:27:39.300
why can't the door be opened?

00:27:51.580 --> 00:27:52.180
How come?

00:27:52.820 --> 00:27:54.460
It functioned properly when I came here.

00:28:01.780 --> 00:28:02.620
I don't know.

00:28:03.020 --> 00:28:04.020
I know nothing about it.

00:28:08.300 --> 00:28:10.300
Can you come up with any other ways?

00:28:11.660 --> 00:28:12.860
Other ways?

00:28:16.460 --> 00:28:16.860
No, I can't.

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:19.740
What should we do?

00:28:20.500 --> 00:28:21.420
We can't go out.

00:28:23.900 --> 00:28:24.540
Well.

00:28:25.660 --> 00:28:26.500
Shall we have the meal first?

00:28:27.620 --> 00:28:28.340
Anyway,

00:28:28.420 --> 00:28:29.100
you are hungry.

00:28:29.580 --> 00:28:30.180
So am I.

00:28:35.940 --> 00:28:36.340
Fine.

00:28:36.740 --> 00:28:38.380
Then I will go heat the dishes on the table.

00:28:38.860 --> 00:28:39.260
Wait for me.

00:28:39.620 --> 00:28:40.220
Wait for me for a moment.

00:28:40.420 --> 00:28:41.580
Let me do it. You are running a fever.

00:28:41.580 --> 00:28:42.500
It doesn't matter. I'll do it.

00:28:44.300 --> 00:28:45.860
You ran away so quickly.

00:29:16.660 --> 00:29:17.500
Why are you looking at me?

00:29:19.220 --> 00:29:20.140
Will you eat or not?

00:29:21.100 --> 00:29:21.700
If you don't eat, I will leave.

00:29:22.380 --> 00:29:23.140
I will eat. I will eat.

00:29:23.260 --> 00:29:23.700
I'm eating.

00:29:32.540 --> 00:29:33.100
I'm eating.

00:29:36.100 --> 00:29:36.580
I,

00:29:37.060 --> 00:29:37.580
I'm eating.

00:29:37.700 --> 00:29:39.020
I am really eating.

00:29:41.500 --> 00:29:42.860
I just wanted to watch TV in the living room.

00:29:43.700 --> 00:29:44.420
Enjoy the dishes.

00:30:09.620 --> 00:30:10.300
Zhao Fanzhou.

00:30:10.500 --> 00:30:11.060
Yes?

00:30:15.500 --> 00:30:16.860
This drug isn't expired.

00:30:18.220 --> 00:30:19.900
In your opinion,
has Mrs. Zhao misread the words

00:30:19.900 --> 00:30:20.740
or has she done this on purpose?

00:30:44.220 --> 00:30:44.860
I really

00:30:45.260 --> 00:30:45.900
have no idea.

00:31:11.740 --> 00:31:12.580
Have you finished taking the temperature?

00:31:12.900 --> 00:31:13.300
Yeah,

00:31:13.540 --> 00:31:14.140
I have.

00:31:18.660 --> 00:31:19.820
38.3 degrees Celsius.

00:31:20.420 --> 00:31:21.420
Hurry to sleep for a while.

00:31:21.620 --> 00:31:23.180
I will come to check
whether your fever is brought down later.

00:31:23.700 --> 00:31:24.780
It's all right. I am not sleepy.

00:31:26.620 --> 00:31:27.060
Go to sleep!

00:31:28.180 --> 00:31:28.580
OK.

00:31:36.580 --> 00:31:37.100
Zhou Xiao.

00:31:38.780 --> 00:31:39.340
What?

00:31:41.460 --> 00:31:41.980
You...

00:31:42.860 --> 00:31:44.260
You won't leave, will you?

00:31:47.500 --> 00:31:47.940
I won't.

00:31:48.380 --> 00:31:48.780
Really?

00:31:50.620 --> 00:31:51.900
I must go out first if I want to leave.

00:31:54.940 --> 00:31:55.420
Zhou Xiao.

00:31:56.220 --> 00:31:57.180
What is it this time?

00:31:59.140 --> 00:31:59.700
Could you

00:32:00.020 --> 00:32:01.140
help me

00:32:01.140 --> 00:32:03.100
fetch my earphones
from my backpack downstairs.

00:32:03.380 --> 00:32:05.500
I can't fall asleep
without listening to a song.

00:32:06.620 --> 00:32:07.780
OK, young master.

00:32:09.980 --> 00:32:10.700
So troublesome!

00:32:41.020 --> 00:32:41.900
Should I

00:32:43.060 --> 00:32:44.180
forgive you or not?

00:33:05.780 --> 00:33:07.100
Sweet voice print?

00:33:09.660 --> 00:33:10.940
Is it for voice print identification?

00:33:13.300 --> 00:33:14.140
Is it used to crack a case?

00:33:50.380 --> 00:33:50.780
You...

00:33:51.380 --> 00:33:52.260
You can't misunderstand me.

00:33:52.740 --> 00:33:54.340
I was just curious about
what you are listening to.

00:33:59.500 --> 00:33:59.980
I...

00:34:01.420 --> 00:34:02.260
I am listening to nothing special.

00:34:02.780 --> 00:34:03.620
Nothing special?

00:34:04.020 --> 00:34:04.820
Then why can't you

00:34:05.260 --> 00:34:06.180
fall asleep without listening to it.

00:34:06.780 --> 00:34:07.620
I heard it.

00:34:08.220 --> 00:34:09.020
It is the snore.

00:34:09.820 --> 00:34:10.420
Whose snore is it?

00:34:21.820 --> 00:34:22.500
My snore?

00:34:27.380 --> 00:34:28.380
When did you record it?

00:34:42.620 --> 00:34:43.180
Delete it!

00:34:43.780 --> 00:34:44.340
No, I can't.

00:34:45.140 --> 00:34:47.220
If it is deleted,
I won't be able to fall asleep later.

00:34:52.940 --> 00:34:53.620
Where are you going?

00:34:54.060 --> 00:34:55.140
I will break the window to escape.

00:34:56.340 --> 00:34:57.020
Go back to your bed.

00:35:05.060 --> 00:35:05.740
Zhou Xiao.

00:35:06.340 --> 00:35:07.060
Zhou Xiao.

00:35:20.220 --> 00:35:21.060
Take your temperature again.

00:35:23.700 --> 00:35:24.260
OK.

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:22.380
Give it to me.

00:36:23.700 --> 00:36:24.140
Hmm.

00:36:30.380 --> 00:36:30.980
Whoa!

00:36:31.500 --> 00:36:32.540
42 degrees Celsius.

00:36:33.060 --> 00:36:34.300
The thermometer will explode due to the heat.

00:36:35.500 --> 00:36:36.100
Zhao Fanzhou.

00:36:39.060 --> 00:36:39.940
Are you fooling me?

00:36:40.380 --> 00:36:41.220
Do you think I am a fool?

00:36:47.700 --> 00:36:48.380
I am sorry!

00:36:48.500 --> 00:36:49.220
Let go of me!

00:36:50.100 --> 00:36:50.460
No, I won't.

00:36:50.780 --> 00:36:51.540
Let go of me.

00:36:51.740 --> 00:36:52.620
I won't.

00:36:53.420 --> 00:36:54.420
Let go of me!

00:37:00.260 --> 00:37:01.460
What do you want on earth?

00:37:11.380 --> 00:37:12.060
Sorry.

00:37:12.740 --> 00:37:13.540
I was wrong.

00:37:15.180 --> 00:37:17.380
Except saying sorry, what else can you say?

00:37:19.020 --> 00:37:20.060
Could you please forgive me?

00:37:22.260 --> 00:37:22.860
No, I can't.

00:37:26.020 --> 00:37:27.180
I will change for sure.

00:37:28.900 --> 00:37:29.700
I don't care.

00:37:38.380 --> 00:37:39.820
Please give me another chance.

00:37:56.100 --> 00:37:57.220
Just let me go.

00:38:00.940 --> 00:38:02.300
I won't let you leave me again.

00:38:26.400 --> 00:38:28.740
Please give one more chance.

00:39:05.300 --> 00:39:05.820
No need.

00:39:11.020 --> 00:39:11.820
If you are sleepy,

00:39:12.660 --> 00:39:13.740
you can sleep in the guest room.

00:39:14.780 --> 00:39:16.620
Mrs. Zhao said she would come back
in a while, right?

00:39:17.020 --> 00:39:18.900
I will wait for her return
and go back to school for sleep.

00:39:19.780 --> 00:39:21.340
She said this an hour ago, but...

00:39:34.260 --> 00:39:35.020
Zhou Xiao.

00:39:35.460 --> 00:39:37.180
I was locked in the exhibition hall.

00:39:37.180 --> 00:39:38.340
Do you have the key with you?

00:39:38.660 --> 00:39:39.860
Come to open the door for me.

00:39:41.060 --> 00:39:41.660
Lu,

00:39:43.900 --> 00:39:45.100
I am coming. Don't be scared.

00:39:48.780 --> 00:39:50.060
What is the sound in your place?

00:39:52.060 --> 00:39:53.500
Xie Yixing is banging on the door.

00:39:55.380 --> 00:39:56.100
Come quickly.

00:39:56.100 --> 00:39:58.380
If you don't, Xie Yixing will have to
compensate for a broken door.

00:39:58.900 --> 00:40:00.300
Well, wait for a moment.

00:40:00.340 --> 00:40:01.380
I, I will go there in a while.

00:40:02.900 --> 00:40:03.580
I will hang up. I got to go.

00:40:04.100 --> 00:40:04.460
Goodbye!

00:40:05.260 --> 00:40:06.020
Listen to me.

00:40:06.300 --> 00:40:07.380
Now, the most important thing for you

00:40:07.660 --> 00:40:08.900
is to keep calm.

00:40:08.980 --> 00:40:09.540
Do you understand?

00:40:09.820 --> 00:40:10.380
Listen to me.

00:40:12.900 --> 00:40:14.180
Stop bumping against the door.

00:40:14.180 --> 00:40:15.100
Zhou Xiao will be here soon.

00:40:17.180 --> 00:40:18.060
Stay quiet for a while.

00:40:22.420 --> 00:40:23.260
Don't be scared.

00:40:23.900 --> 00:40:24.940
I will be here with you.

00:40:27.020 --> 00:40:27.540
What should I do?

00:40:27.900 --> 00:40:29.420
Lu is locked in the exhibition hall.

00:40:29.700 --> 00:40:30.900
I have the spare key with me.

00:40:31.140 --> 00:40:32.340
I must go back to unlock the door for her.

00:40:35.140 --> 00:40:35.820
What?

00:40:36.500 --> 00:40:37.300
What are you doing?

00:40:37.740 --> 00:40:38.860
Looking for a way out.

00:40:39.100 --> 00:40:40.220
We must figure out a way.

00:40:43.060 --> 00:40:43.580
Let's go.

00:40:43.660 --> 00:40:44.380
Where?

00:40:45.380 --> 00:40:46.340
Go unlock the door.

00:40:46.700 --> 00:40:48.060
The door is locked. Don't you know?

00:40:48.300 --> 00:40:49.420
I can unlock the door with my mobile phone.

00:40:56.500 --> 00:40:57.180
I swear.

00:40:57.700 --> 00:40:58.660
Except this,

00:40:58.940 --> 00:40:59.940
I really know nothing

00:41:00.060 --> 00:41:00.900
about other things.

00:41:42.140 --> 00:41:42.940
Lazy Ling,

00:41:44.260 --> 00:41:45.980
why have you got up so early?

00:41:47.380 --> 00:41:47.980
Wei,

00:41:48.140 --> 00:41:49.460
I will study together with you.

00:41:49.740 --> 00:41:50.700
From today onward,

00:41:50.780 --> 00:41:52.260
you will be my role model.

00:41:52.580 --> 00:41:53.740
I will learn from you

00:41:53.740 --> 00:41:55.180
and become a positive
and hard-working person.

00:41:55.620 --> 00:41:57.180
I will study for a master's degree
and a doctoral degree.

00:41:57.540 --> 00:41:58.820
I will prove myself to Fang Wei.

00:41:59.140 --> 00:41:59.940
But...

00:42:00.020 --> 00:42:01.220
But what?

00:42:01.500 --> 00:42:03.300
I am no longer the lazy person I used to be.

00:42:03.340 --> 00:42:05.540
Now I fear no hardship and difficulty.

00:42:06.860 --> 00:42:07.460
I didn't mean that.

00:42:07.980 --> 00:42:10.020
I meant I have to go outside of the school

00:42:10.460 --> 00:42:12.300
to attend the dance lectures today.

00:42:14.100 --> 00:42:14.660
Hmm.

00:42:17.460 --> 00:42:19.060
You can study by yourself now.

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:20.460
I will come to join you later.

00:42:21.580 --> 00:42:22.140
No need.

00:42:22.180 --> 00:42:23.220
I will go have a sleep.

00:42:23.380 --> 00:42:24.260
I will have a sleep first.

00:42:24.820 --> 00:42:25.500
What?

00:42:29.340 --> 00:42:30.220
Zhou Xiao.

00:42:31.340 --> 00:42:32.140
Zhou Xiao.

00:42:40.620 --> 00:42:41.380
Zhou Xiao.

00:42:41.700 --> 00:42:42.740
Zhou Xiao, get up.

00:42:43.580 --> 00:42:45.540
You asked me to wake you up, right?

00:42:45.540 --> 00:42:47.260
You said you would accompany Zhao Fanzhou
to attend class.

00:42:49.620 --> 00:42:50.180
Right.

00:42:58.540 --> 00:42:59.980
I'd better give it up.

00:43:00.220 --> 00:43:00.780
Ah?

00:43:02.980 --> 00:43:04.660
I don't want to accompany Zhao Fanzhou
to attend class now.

00:43:05.060 --> 00:43:05.700
You

00:43:05.940 --> 00:43:07.220
have made up with each other, right?

00:43:10.020 --> 00:43:11.220
What is wrong, Zhou Xiao?

00:43:16.300 --> 00:43:16.860
Wei,

00:43:17.500 --> 00:43:19.020
do you know this feeling?

00:43:20.060 --> 00:43:21.060
After two people in love

00:43:21.300 --> 00:43:22.780
break up and then make up with each other,

00:43:23.260 --> 00:43:24.060
there will be

00:43:24.620 --> 00:43:26.980
an ineffable estrangement
and embarrassment between them.

00:43:28.740 --> 00:43:29.340
They will

00:43:29.420 --> 00:43:30.820
feel worried and can't dispel this feeling.

00:43:30.940 --> 00:43:31.620
They will fear that the other person

00:43:31.940 --> 00:43:33.980
may want to split up again suddenly.

00:43:34.260 --> 00:43:35.380
Therefore, they dare not give it all again.

00:43:37.620 --> 00:43:39.540
All in all, I don't feel comfortable
in this relationship now.

00:43:39.540 --> 00:43:39.900
I,

00:43:40.340 --> 00:43:42.220
I dare not face him again.

00:43:42.900 --> 00:43:43.740
What should I do?

00:43:43.900 --> 00:43:44.740
Do you understand?

00:43:49.220 --> 00:43:50.420
How should I describe it?

00:43:53.340 --> 00:43:54.900
It's a feeling that I worry about
personal gains and losses.

00:43:59.540 --> 00:44:00.780
Why can't you understand?

00:44:02.020 --> 00:44:02.820
Perhaps,

00:44:03.580 --> 00:44:05.380
it is because I have never been in love.

00:44:08.260 --> 00:44:08.940
Yes. Exactly.

00:44:10.860 --> 00:44:13.460
Well, my rough idea is that

00:44:15.820 --> 00:44:17.500
I dare not get too close
to the person I hold dearest.

00:44:18.340 --> 00:44:18.980
Do you know?

00:44:20.340 --> 00:44:21.100
It is that kind of...

00:44:22.100 --> 00:44:22.860
Shut up!

00:44:22.900 --> 00:44:23.940
What nonsense!

00:44:24.060 --> 00:44:25.220
You have made up with each other for real.

00:44:25.220 --> 00:44:26.260
Don't show off your love here.

00:44:26.260 --> 00:44:26.780
Hey, guys!

00:44:28.580 --> 00:44:30.420
Why are you making so much noise?

00:44:31.620 --> 00:44:33.740
Can you allow me to sleep a little longer?

00:44:33.900 --> 00:44:36.060
I'm having a date with Xie Yixing later.

00:44:36.580 --> 00:44:37.780
There is nothing special about a date.

00:44:38.140 --> 00:44:38.820
Wei,

00:44:38.940 --> 00:44:40.180
I don't support you to be in love.

00:44:40.220 --> 00:44:41.300
A love relationship is meaningless.

00:44:42.340 --> 00:44:42.900
Wei,

00:44:43.500 --> 00:44:44.860
I support you to be in love.

00:44:45.100 --> 00:44:46.420
A romantic relationship makes people happy.

00:44:46.540 --> 00:44:47.420
I am against it.

00:44:47.460 --> 00:44:48.220
I am for it.

00:44:48.220 --> 00:44:48.980
Shut up!

00:44:49.020 --> 00:44:49.660
You shut up!

00:44:49.740 --> 00:44:50.700
One, two, three! Shut up together.

00:44:50.860 --> 00:44:52.340
One, two, three.

00:45:01.500 --> 00:45:02.820
Will you get up or not?

00:45:04.860 --> 00:45:06.340
No, I won't. Good night!

00:45:11.860 --> 00:45:13.900
Seeing what my roommates look like
when they are in love,

00:45:14.300 --> 00:45:15.700
who still dares to fall in love?

00:45:21.780 --> 00:45:23.700
(Next Episode)
Zhu Lu, I want to tell you that

00:45:24.100 --> 00:45:25.460
I am very happy to be in love with you.

00:45:26.980 --> 00:45:27.540
It has been a long time.

00:45:27.940 --> 00:45:28.820
Yes, it has been a long time.

00:45:29.140 --> 00:45:30.340
Haven't they broken up with each other?

00:45:30.620 --> 00:45:32.500
But they have got back together,
haven't they?

00:45:33.300 --> 00:45:33.820
Dad.

